{"tid":1629343,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇斯克查：時代不同了，紅魔輝煌的歲月已經過去了，球隊需要重建。我們給年青人機會","createTime":"2019-10-06T08:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:15:29.000Z","uid":103207,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"80fb1c9a8ae2808b4e7c0f1f3d9451c6a9ff1a28","tid":1629343,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:28:23.000Z","msg":"曼聯教練<span style=\"color: red;\">蘇斯克查告誡球迷，時代不同了，紅魔輝煌的歲月已經過去了，現在球隊需要重建。</span><br />\n<br />\n  「<span style=\"color: red;\">我們現在不是生活在90年代，</span>」蘇帥說，「現在是一個不同的時代了，我們在建設的是一個不同的團體。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我們知道會有起起伏伏，但我準備好了，要看著這些年青人成長綻放。<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有多少像我們這種級別的球會，能夠這樣給年青人機會。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n  「他們有機會冒頭，我們確信，其中一些人將成為未來一支成功球隊的一部分。」"},{"pid":"3fd29afe1d614a4645e2074cfdb54cb23ace4fc9","tid":1629343,"uid":54557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"係咩級別?<br />\n英超中遊球隊?"},{"pid":"50f3ce38ef46f558b5b8c7cd10d9ed6e1b04712e","tid":1629343,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1aca9541d740cce6b2da125a8b6ff95a87a27f","tid":1629343,"uid":25228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:56:49.000Z","msg":"冇人用就話比機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344e06a584fb01dd43db901ab82d7e9f2d3381d7","tid":1629343,"uid":191926,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:58:36.000Z","msg":"呢句野咁香港feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過曼聯反映左 制度唔改變 <br />\n邊個做特首都係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係曼聯迷<br />\n<br />\n但都知道下<br />\n依家曼聯高層<br />\n重商業  行政總裁唔識波<br />\n<br />\n同香港的情況一樣<br />\n中共唔想認識香港<br />\n淨係想利用香港搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係政治體制無任何改革<br />\n (例好多人要求的體育總監)<